                        "<div style='text-align: justify;'><ul><li><b>Gametic Fusion:</b> Combining DNA from two different individuals.</li><li><b>Recombination:</b> Shuffling of genes during meiosis creates unique offspring.</li><li><b>Impact:</b> Greater variation ensures that some individuals can survive environmental shifts, driving <b>natural selection</b> and helping the species evolve faster.</li></ul></div>",
                        "<div style='text-align: center; margin: 15px 0;'><img src='data:image/jpeg;base64,' style='width: 100%; max-width: 380px; height: auto; border-radius: 8px;' alt='Variation' /></div>"
